Package io.github.dalayach.Print_tools

Contains the implementation of the Print_tools package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Build_strings
    Builds Strings using precalculated values and String.format().
    Helper_functions
    Provides helper functions for the other classes to extend/use.
    String_printer
    This is the String_printer itself.
    Test_for_Build_strings
    Tests Build_strings functions individually for their individual traits.
    Test_for_Helper_functions
    Tests Helper_functions functions individually for their individual traits.
    Test_for_String_printer
    Tests String_printer functions for their ability to provide correctly formatted strings, account for new lines accurately, and to ensure that the shortened version of each print function works as expected.

Package io.github.dalayach.Print_tools Description

Contains the implementation of the Print_tools package. All classes should refer to this package.
